                                    <locus from="1" to="105">ff. 1-105</locus>
                                    <p>The quires have been twice signed with letters (see foll. 16, 46, and 56), but at neither time correctly.</p>
                                </foliation>
                                <collation>
                                    <p>Originally the book was made up of 13 quires</p>
