                                 <locus from="1" to="105">ff. 1-105</locus>
                                 <desc>The character is a good, regular Estrangela of the <origDate notBefore="0500" notAfter="0700">vith or viith cent.</origDate></desc>
                             </handNote>
                             <handNote xml:id="handnote2" scope="minor" script="Estrangelo" medium="unknown">
                                 <locus from="1" to="105">ff. 1-105</locus>
                                 <p>They have been twice signed with letters (see foll.<locus from="16" to="16">16</locus>, 
                                     <locus from="46" to="46">46</locus>, and <locus from="56" to="56">56</locus>), but at neither time correctly.</p>
                             </handNote>
                             <handNote xml:id="handnote3" scope="minor" script="Estrangelo" medium="unknown">
                                 <locus from="1" to="105">ff. 1-105</locus>
                                 <p>Vowels have sometimes been added by a later hand (ܰ, ܶ, ܺ, ܳ, , , ). </p>
                             </handNote>
